Name: Jade
Desc: A senior manager in the IPC Strategic Investment Department and one of the Ten Stonehearts, known for her cornerstone "Jade of Credit."\nA cold and elegant moneylender, she is skilled at understanding the human heart, with a personal hobby called "Bonajade Exchange."\nShe's willing to wait patiently for high-value acquisitions and adept at extracting value from seemingly destitute clients.

1.Name: Altruism? Nevertheless Tradable
1.Desc: The follow-up attack DMG from Jade's Talent increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. Every time Jade gets Charged, she additionally gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> point(s) of Charge.

2.Name: Morality? Herein Authenticated
2.Desc: When there are <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> stacks of Pawned Asset, Jade's CRIT Rate increases by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.

3.Name: Honesty? Soon Mortgaged
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

4.Name: Sincerity? Put Option Only
4.Desc: When using Ultimate, the DMG Jade deals ignores <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of enemy targets' DEF, lasting for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

5.Name: Hope? Hitherto Forfeited
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

6.Name: Equity? Pending Sponsorship
6.Desc: When there are Debt Collector allies on the field, Jade's Quantum RES PEN increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>, and Jade gains the Debt Collector state.

131401.Name: Lash of Riches
131401.Desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Jade's ATK to a single target enemy, and Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Jade's ATK to adjacent enemies.

131402.Name: Acquisition Surety
131402.Desc:
Makes a single target ally become a Debt Collector and increases their SPD by <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak>, lasting for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s).
After a Debt Collector attacks, deals 1 instance of <u>Additional</u> Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> of Jade's ATK to each enemy target hit, and consumes the Debt Collector's HP by an amount equal to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of their Max HP. If their current HP is insufficient, reduces their HP to 1.
If Jade becomes a Debt Collector, she cannot gain the SPD boost effect, and her attacks do not consume HP.
When a Debt Collector exists on the field, Jade cannot use her Skill. At the start of Jade's every turn, the Debt Collector's duration reduces by 1.

131403.Name: Vow of the Deep
131403.Desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> of Jade's ATK to all enemies. At the same time, enhances <u>follow-up attack</u> from Jade's Talent, increasing the follow-up attack's DMG multiplier by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color>. This enhancing effect can activate <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> time(s).

131404.Name: Fang of Flare Flaying
131404.Desc: After Jade or an ally that had become the Debt Collector attacks, Jade gains 1 Charge for each enemy target attacked. When the Charge reaches <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak>, consume <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> Charges to launch <u>follow-up attack</u> 1 time, dealing Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#5[i]%</unbreak></color> of Jade's ATK to all enemies. This <u>follow-up attack</u> does not generate Charge.\nJade immediately gains <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> stack(s) of Pawned Asset when launching her Talent's <u>follow-up attack</u>, with each stack of Pawned Asset increasing her CRIT DMG by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak></color>. This effect can stack up to <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> times.

131406.Name: Attack
131406.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

131407.Name: Visionary Predation
131407.Desc: After using the Technique, inflicts enemies within a set area with Blind Fealty for <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> second(s). Enemies inflicted with Blind Fealty will not actively attack allies. When entering battle via actively attacking enemies inflicted with Blind Fealty, all enemies with Blind Fealty will enter combat simultaneously. Deals Quantum DMG equal to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of Jade's ATK to all enemies, and immediately gains <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> stack(s) of Pawned Asset.

1.PointDesc: When enemy targets enter combat, Jade gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> stack(s) of Pawned Asset. When a Debt Collector ally's turn starts, Jade additionally gains <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> stack(s) of Pawned Asset.
When the battle starts, Jade's action is advanced forward by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.
Each stack of the Talent's Pawned Asset additionally increases Jade's ATK by <unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak>.
